# Canonical quarantine path per canon-proc-004 §2. External material resides
# here and is never tracked as part of the Republic's corpus until ingestion
# per §5. The .gitkeep marker is retained so the directory exists in fresh
# clones; all other contents are ignored.
external/*
!external/.gitkeep
